{"id":1253263634,"question_id":8,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1Â month","timestamp":1715233525,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"1 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1253263634/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"42.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int myAtoi(String s) {\n\n        int res = 0 ;\n\n        s = s.trim();\n\n        int max = Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n        int min = Integer.MIN_VALUE;\n\n        int len = s.length();\n\n        if(len==0) return 0;\n\n        \n\n        int i = 0;\n        boolean sign = false;\n        if(s.charAt(0)=='-'){\n            i=1;\n            sign = true;\n        }\n\n        if(s.charAt(0)=='+')\n            i=1;\n\n        for(; i<len; i++){\n            if(s.charAt(i)<'0' || s.charAt(i)>'9') break;\n\n            if(res>max/10 || (res==max/10 && (s.charAt(i)-'0')>max%10))\n                return sign ? min : max;\n\n            res = res*10 + s.charAt(i)-'0';\n        }\n\n        return sign ? -res : res;\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
